Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米庫里歐……萊拉……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因為高燒昏睡了三天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有三天？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是因為史雷你成為了我的容器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是有艾莉莎幫忙 還不知道該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了！艾莉莎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了……你醒了……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你這麼有食慾 應該不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉莎你一直在照顧我吧？謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才應該道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你拔出湖之乙女的聖劍時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令那場祭典中的暴動平息下來時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心裡也無比激動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我最想說的話就是「謝謝」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為表示我的感謝之情 我希望你收下這件東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.29,0:01:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史雷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
